  "Description": {
    "English": "Gently detaches the starship from gravitational fields, lifting it toward the stars.<br> <br>The well hungers for <span class=\"name name-special\">pugneum</span> or <span class=\"name name-special\">radiant shards</span>, and must be sufficiently fueled before launch.<br> <br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span> to take off from planet.<br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> to initiate in-flight speed boost.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "将飞船轻柔牵离重力场，并将其“托”向星辰。<br><br>反重力井需要<span class=\"name name-special\">普茵</span>或<span class=\"name name-special\">光耀碎片</span>，并且只有在填补足够燃料之后才能够启动。<br><br>长按<span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span>升空并离开星球。<br>长按<span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span>在飞行中进行速度提升。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使太空船輕巧地脫離重力場，飛入群星之中。<br><br>這口井渴望著<span class=\"name name-special\">搏</span>或<span class=\"name name-special\">發光裂片</span>的能量，發射前必須補充足夠的燃料。<br><br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">THRUST</span> 自星球起飛。<br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">BOOST</span> 啟動飛行加速功能。"
  },
